@startuml
title LifeDuo - Comunicação Geral do Sistema (Parte 2)

skinparam backgroundColor #FAFAFA
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 1.5
skinparam sequenceParticipantBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam sequenceParticipantBackgroundColor #F8BBD0
skinparam sequenceActorBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam sequenceActorBackgroundColor #F48FB1
skinparam sequenceLifeLineBorderColor #AD1457
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #880E4F
skinparam sequenceMessageFontColor #880E4F
skinparam noteBorderColor #AD1457
skinparam noteBackgroundColor #FCE4EC
skinparam noteFontColor #880E4F
skinparam databaseBorderColor #C2185B
skinparam databaseBackgroundColor #F8BBD0

actor "Parceiro A" as A
actor "Parceiro B" as B
participant "App Mobile" as Mobile
participant "API Gateway" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as DB
participant "Socket.IO" as WS
participant "NotificationService" as Notif
actor "Administrador" as Admin

== Fluxo Secundário: Metas e Presentes ==

A -> Mobile : 26. criarMetaCompartilhada(titulo, valor)
Mobile -> API : 27. POST /goals
API -> DB : 28. salvarMeta()
DB --> API : 29. metaSalva
API -> Notif : 30. sendPush(coupleId)
Notif -> B : 31. notificarNovaMeta()
API --> Mobile : 32. 201 + metaCriada

A -> Mobile : 33. enviarPresente(giftType)
Mobile -> API : 34. POST /gifts
API -> DB : 35. salvarPresente()
DB --> API : 36. presenteSalvo
API -> Notif : 37. publishEvent(GiftSent)
Notif -> WS : 38. emitRealtime()
WS -> B : 39. animacaoSurpresa()
API --> Mobile : 40. 201 + giftConfirmado

== Fluxo Secundário: Lugares e Bem-estar ==

A -> Mobile : 41. salvarLugar(nome, coords)
Mobile -> API : 42. POST /places
API -> DB : 43. salvarLugar()
DB --> API : 44. lugarSalvo
API -> DB : 45. verificarMatch(coupleId)
DB --> API : 46. matchEncontrado
API -> Notif : 47. sendPush(matchEncontrado)
Notif -> B : 48. notificarMatch()
API --> Mobile : 49. 201 + lugarSalvo

A -> Mobile : 50. registrarSaude(dados, consent)
Mobile -> API : 51. POST /wellness
API -> DB : 52. encryptData(), salvarRegistro()
DB --> API : 53. registroSalvo
API -> Notif : 54. sendPush(coupleId)
Notif -> B : 55. notificacaoSutil()
API --> Mobile : 56. 201 + registroConfirmado

== Fluxo Administrativo ==

Admin -> API : 57. GET /moderation/reports
API -> DB : 58. listarReports()
DB --> API : 59. listaReports
API --> Admin : 60. relatorioExibido

Admin -> API : 61. POST /moderation/approve(reportId)
API -> DB : 62. atualizarStatus(aprovado)
DB --> API : 63. statusAtualizado
API -> Notif : 64. sendPush(criador)
API --> Admin : 65. aprovacaoConfirmada

@enduml